。<br />\n如果火影一開始無第七班同卡卡西打然後分飯盒食呢一幕，<br />\n打白+再不斬時，佐助肯為鳴人死然後鳴人第一次變九尾呢段情節就唔合理。<br />\n同上，無咗呢段，中忍考試鳴人追佐助既理由亦都變得唔合理。<br />\n<br />\n故事係要一層一層咁鋪排上去，唔係某啲情節失驚無神湊上去就得，呢個毛病係好多日漫都有。<br />\n以前JUMP 係做得好好。雖然亦都有人話令好多劇情公式化，<br />\n但反觀宜家既鬼滅、咒術回戰都係有呢啲情節問題，令到個故事唔吸引同濫情。<br />\n我覺得係JUMP 宜家呢一代既編輯全有責任。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:32:40.000Z","msg":"呢套交代劇情真係差d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實個咒術系統都係任佢吹無乜核心支撐"},{"pid":"b76805386da0089017a03a432e532dcf0870f992","tid":2438954,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67acac8cf62f2160105852f9ea142249e8f9a784","tid":2438954,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"95dabedcfc31ac1906db785c33059a89c0dd1a15","tid":2438954,"uid":15376,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"bc7c097f6625e8eeec9514b2eca00f6dadb2be46","tid":2438954,"uid":256210,"like":24,"dislike":26,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"設定太似火影"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:57:01.000Z","msg":"第七班抄到一模一樣咁濟添啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:27:07.000Z","msg":"五條悟 根本就係卡卡西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"卡卡西咁垃圾就唔好提<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd70b16c951b48c754c43ae5e522830668e3b621","tid":2438954,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b76805386da0089017a03a432e532dcf0870f992","tid":2438954,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67acac8cf62f2160105852f9ea142249e8f9a784","tid":2438954,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"95dabedcfc31ac1906db785c33059a89c0dd1a15","tid":2438954,"uid":15376,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:57:01.000Z","msg":"第七班抄到一模一樣咁濟添啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T04:27:07.000Z","msg":"五條悟 根本就係卡卡西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2